title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Boudreau/Mileski/Russo/Ramsey
description: PA and Nordo are back inside the penalty box of the Xcel Energy Center! The FAN's Brandon Mileski co-hosts the first hour which features Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau. The Athletic's Michael Russo stop by during the second hour of the show before K102's Rachel Ramsey joins the guys in the penalty box in the final hour of #92Noon!
